properties.Name: AssetCostType
properties.Description:
A type of cost that may be assigned to applied to an Asset for the associated period.

Ex:
- Freight-in cost
- Installation cost
- Acquisition cost
- Book cost
- Net Purchase cost

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Asset Cost Type.

Columns.Description: The name of an Asset Cost Type.

Columns.Name: AssetCostTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an Asset Cost Type.
